034/**
035 * RFC 2301: File Format for Internet Fax.
036 * <p>
037 * www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2301.txt
038 * </p>
039 * <p>
040 * Also subsumes "The spirit of TIFF class F"
041 * </p>
042 * <p>
043 * https://cool.culturalheritage.org/bytopic/imaging/std/tiff-f.html
044 * </p>
045 */
046public final class Rfc2301TagConstants {
047
048    public static final TagInfoShortOrLong TIFF_TAG_BAD_FAX_LINES = new TagInfoShortOrLong("BadFaxLines", 0x0146, 1, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);

050    public static final TagInfoShort TIFF_TAG_CLEAN_FAX_DATA = new TagInfoShort("CleanFaxData", 0x0147, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
051    public static final int CLEAN_FAX_DATA_VALUE_CLEAN = 0;
052    public static final int CLEAN_FAX_DATA_VALUE_REGENERATED = 1;
053    public static final int CLEAN_FAX_DATA_VALUE_UNCLEAN = 2;
054
055    public static final TagInfoShortOrLong TIFF_TAG_CONSECUTIVE_BAD_FAX_LINES = new TagInfoShortOrLong("ConsecutiveBadFaxLines", 0x0148, 1,
056            TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
057
058    public static final TagInfoDirectory TIFF_TAG_GLOBAL_PARAMETERS_IFD = new TagInfoDirectory("GlobalParametersIFD", 0x0190,
059            TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
060
061    public static final TagInfoLong TIFF_TAG_PROFILE_TYPE = new TagInfoLong("ProfileType", 0x0191, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
062    public static final int PROFILE_TYPE_VALUE_UNSPECIFIED = 0;
063    public static final int PROFILE_TYPE_VALUE_GROUP_3_FAX = 1;
064
065    public static final TagInfoByte TIFF_TAG_FAX_PROFILE = new TagInfoByte("FaxProfile", 0x0192, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
066    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_UNKNOWN = 0;
067    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_MINIMAL_B_AND_W_LOSSLESS_S = 1;
068    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_EXTENDED_B_AND_W_LOSSLESS_F = 2;
069    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_LOSSLESS_JBIG_B_AND_W_J = 3;
070    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_LOSSY_COLOR_AND_GRAYSCALE_C = 4;
071    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_LOSSLESS_COLOR_AND_GRAYSCALE_L = 5;
072    public static final int FAX_PROFILE_VALUE_MIXED_RASTER_CONTENT_M = 6;
073
074    public static final TagInfoLong TIFF_TAG_CODING_METHODS = new TagInfoLong("CodingMethods", 0x0193, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
075    public static final int CODING_METHODS_VALUE_T4_1D = 2;
076    public static final int CODING_METHODS_VALUE_T4_2D = 4;
077    public static final int CODING_METHODS_VALUE_T6 = 8;
078    public static final int CODING_METHODS_VALUE_T82_T85 = 16;
079    public static final int CODING_METHODS_VALUE_T81 = 32;
080    public static final int CODING_METHODS_VALUE_T82_T43 = 64;
081
082    public static final TagInfoBytes TIFF_TAG_VERSION_YEAR = new TagInfoBytes("VersionYear", 0x0194, 4, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
083
084    public static final TagInfoByte TIFF_TAG_MODE_NUMBER = new TagInfoByte("ModeNumber", 0x0195, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
085
086    public static final TagInfoRationals TIFF_TAG_DECODE = new TagInfoRationals("Decode", 0x01b1, -1, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
087
088    public static final TagInfoShorts TIFF_TAG_DEFAULT_IMAGE_COLOR = new TagInfoShorts("DefaultImageColor", 0x01b2, -1,
089            TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
090
091    public static final TagInfoLongs TIFF_TAG_STRIP_ROW_COUNTS = new TagInfoLongs("StripRowCounts", 0x022f, -1, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
092
093    public static final TagInfoShortOrLong TIFF_TAG_IMAGE_LAYER = new TagInfoShortOrLong("ImageLayer", 0x87ac, 2, TiffDirectoryType.EXIF_DIRECTORY_UNKNOWN);
094
095    public static final List<TagInfo> ALL_RFC_2301_TAGS = Collections.unmodifiableList(Arrays.asList(TIFF_TAG_BAD_FAX_LINES, TIFF_TAG_CLEAN_FAX_DATA,
096            TIFF_TAG_CONSECUTIVE_BAD_FAX_LINES, TIFF_TAG_GLOBAL_PARAMETERS_IFD, TIFF_TAG_PROFILE_TYPE, TIFF_TAG_FAX_PROFILE, TIFF_TAG_CODING_METHODS,

099    private Rfc2301TagConstants() {
